  "meta": { "description": "Every 30 min, run the VYREX agentic AI analyst (POST /agent/triage) — a self-hosted Ollama LLM reasons over the open, already-explained findings and records ESCALATE/MONITOR/DISMISS decisions with reasoning — then dispatch the escalations to channels. The agent only proposes; containment stays behind two-person approval. To wire the *native* n8n AI Agent node (Ollama model + VYREX HTTP tools) instead, see docs/N8N-AUTOMATION.md." }
